Oyo State governor, Engr Seyi Makinde, has approved the appointment of two aides to work with the Office of the Chief of Staff to the Governor. They are Adeyemo Adedeji Ola, Special Assistant (Political), and Clement Oyerinde Ige, Special Assistant (Special Duties). The governor, while congratulating the aides, urged them to see their appointment as a call to service.The appointments are with immediate effect.